    "discriminators": [
     "A whoopee cushion, a raspberry or a flarp is a buzzing reed: low, harmonic-rich, sustained and steadier in pitch than the real thing — a slightly more tonal, more periodic buzz than FARTS-REAL.",
     "That is a tendency, not a test. A mouth fart and a real fart are the same physics — a slack aperture buzzing under pressure — so the real/fake split is semantic. Let the filename decide.",
     "Against HUMAN-BURP: farts sit lower and carry no vocal-tract formant structure."
    ],
